00:10:34.350 --> 00:10:43.910
So having a disability or some
sort of accessibility need

00:10:43.910 --> 00:10:46.893
can be super, super
difficult or make

00:10:46.893 --> 00:10:48.560
using your phone
super, super difficult.

00:10:48.560 --> 00:10:51.210
So adding little tweaks
to your application

00:10:51.210 --> 00:10:55.797
or to your operating system
can make a huge difference.

