00:24:43.710 --> 00:24:44.640
please come find us.

00:24:44.640 --> 00:24:45.880
Come talk to us.

00:24:45.880 --> 00:24:48.540
We'd love to hear why
you prioritized it,

00:24:48.540 --> 00:24:50.910
any insights you can
provide, and partner

00:24:50.910 --> 00:24:53.010
to see how we can bring
that information back

00:24:53.010 --> 00:24:54.660
to the ecosystem.

00:24:54.660 --> 00:24:56.910
And if you walk away with
one thing from this session,

00:24:56.910 --> 00:24:59.070
we hope that it's not
only are you creating

00:24:59.070 --> 00:25:02.160
an experience for folks
with disabilities to have

00:25:02.160 --> 00:25:04.530
an accessible
experience, that bringing

00:25:04.530 --> 00:25:07.110
in these core
functionalities to your app

00:25:07.110 --> 00:25:10.630
will make it a better user
